{"id":8455,"date":"2025-09-22T08:48:37","date_gmt":"2025-09-22T08:48:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/realtrips.in\/?post_type=trip&#038;p=8455"},"modified":"2025-12-04T11:33:58","modified_gmt":"2025-12-04T11:33:58","slug":"short-break-rajasthan","status":"publish","type":"trip","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/trip\/short-break-rajasthan\/","title":{"rendered":"SHORT BREAK RAJASTHAN"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Escape into the royal charm of <strong>Rajasthan<\/strong>, where every fort tells a story and every sunset paints the desert gold. This short yet unforgettable getaway takes you through the <strong>majestic palaces, vibrant bazaars, and desert landscapes<\/strong> that define India\u2019s most regal state.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Escape into the royal charm of Rajasthan, where every fort tells a story and every sunset paints the desert gold. This short yet unforgettable getaway takes you through the majestic palaces, vibrant bazaars, and desert landscapes that define India\u2019s most regal state.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8935,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","destination":[96],"activities":[],"trip_types":[75],"difficulty":[],"trip_tag":[],"wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory":[77],"class_list":["post-8455","trip","type-trip","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","destination-royal-rajasthan","trip_types-customized-domestic-tour","tripcategory-customized-domestic-tour"],"packages_ids":[8456],"trip_extras":[],"cut_off_time":{"enabled":false,"duration":0,"duration_unit":"days"},"booked-seats":[],"code":"WTE-8455","price":22777,"has_sale":false,"sale_price":0,"discount_percent":0,"currency":{"code":"INR","symbol":"&#8377;"},"duration":{"days":6,"nights":5,"duration_unit":"days","duration_type":"days"},"min_pax":1,"max_pax":"","discount_value":0,"discount_label":"&#8377;0 Off","primary_category":27,"available_times":{"type":"default","items":["2021-1-01","2021-2-01","2021-3-01","2021-4-01","2021-5-01","2021-6-01","2021-7-01","2021-8-01","2021-9-01","2021-10-01","2021-11-01","2021-12-01"]},"description":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Experience the essence of Rajasthan in a short yet memorable getaway that blends heritage, culture, and charm. Explore the vibrant streets and majestic palaces of <strong>Jaipur<\/strong>, the Pink City, with its iconic Amber Fort, City Palace, and Hawa Mahal. Take a walk through colorful bazaars filled with handicrafts and traditional Rajasthani flavors. Discover the serenity of <strong>Pushkar<\/strong>, home to the sacred Brahma Temple and holy lake, where spirituality meets cultural vibrance. This short break offers a glimpse into Rajasthan\u2019s royal legacy, colorful traditions, and warm hospitality\u2014perfect for travelers seeking a quick royal escape.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->","cost_includes":" 3 star premium hotel stay\n All transfers and sightseeing by AC Vehicle\n Breakfast, Dinner. Lunch\n Toll Tax\n Parking\n Driver Allowance\nTravel Goodies\n 24 x 7 On tour Assistance\n All cost from EX Destination","cost_excludes":"Any meals other than those mentioned above in inclusions\n Airfare \/ Train Ticket\n GST 5%\n All monument entry Fees\n Any portage at airports and hotels, tips, insurance, wine, mineral water, telephone charges, and all items of personal nature\n Any services not specifically mentioned in the inclusions\nEntrance fees to Monuments & other sightseeing points\nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, vehicle malfunctions, political disturbances, etc.\nAnything not mentioned in inclusions","itineraries":[],"faqs":[{"title":"1. What are the key highlights of this tour? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Jaipur: Amber Fort, City Palace, Hawa Mahal, Jantar Mantar, local bazaars<br>Pushkar (optional): Brahma Temple, Pushkar Lake, colorful streets.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"2. What should I pack for the trip? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Light cottons in summer, light woolens in winter Comfortable footwear for fort visits &amp; walking in bazaars Sunglasses, cap, sunscreen, camera.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"3. Is this package suitable for families and kids?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, Rajasthan is family-friendly. Children especially enjoy fort visits, camel rides, and colorful markets.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"4. What type of accommodation will be provided?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You will stay in neat and comfortable hotels\/resorts with modern amenities. Heritage\/luxury hotel upgrades are available on request.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"5. Are cultural activities included in this package?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cultural shows, folk dance performances, and traditional Rajasthani dinners are optional but can be arranged at an additional cost.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"}],"is_featured":false,"featured_image":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/1-2.png","filesize":538097,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"1-2-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":34339,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1-2-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"1-2-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":15240,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1-2-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"1-2-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":146153,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1-2-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"1-2-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":45086,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/1-2-374x226.png"},"destination-t